WEBVTT

00:04:28.914 --> 00:04:30.405
in your life?

00:04:31.707 --> 00:04:34.383
It's not just another day.

00:04:34.407 --> 00:04:38.245
It's the one day that is given to you:

00:04:38.269 --> 00:04:39.589
today.

00:04:39.613 --> 00:04:41.919
(Music)

00:04:41.943 --> 00:04:43.854
It's given to you.

00:04:44.974 --> 00:04:46.421
It's a gift.

00:04:48.110 --> 00:04:51.214
It's the only gift
that you have right now.

00:04:52.096 --> 00:04:54.977
And the only appropriate response

00:04:55.001 --> 00:04:56.779
is gratefulness.

00:04:58.413 --> 00:05:02.961
(Music)